The Data required can be found using foursquare and a wiki page detailing coordinates of different neighborhoods: 
The Latitude and Longitude of John's address
Neighborhoods close to John
The Indian restaurants located within each neighborhood 
Table with all the neighborhood's individual resturant ratings
Specific venue details - overall ratings, tips, agree counts, disagree counts

Using all this data, you can evaluate the "competition" within neighborhoods near John based on number of Indian 
Restaurants nearby and the number of high rated restaurants in those neighborhoods. Additional info such as specific venue details can be used as a tie breaker.
The neighborhood with the lowest ranking will be the neighborhood John should open his restaurant in. 
